Inflicts regular damage. Hits 25 times in one turn.
Has a 3/8 chance each to hit 2 or 3 times, and a 1/8 chance each to hit 4 or 5 times. Averages to 3 hits per use.

div.div: Sawfox is a colossal simple xenom who loves living in lush surroundings. Its swift movements fling seeds that ricochet with force.
